Discworld room help
shop

.SH Name
.SI 5
shop - a general store
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
buy <object>
sell <object>
browse <object>
list [all]
list <object>
value <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a room help file.

The general store is a place where you can go to buy and sell any sort of
object.  Some of these general stores are specialised in different sorts of
items, like they will only buy jewellery or weapons.  All general stores
will buy objects for much less than they will sell them.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> sell leather jacket
> buy torch
> list
> value shirt
.EI

